        <item>
            <title>香港 16 岁少年夺 Pokémon GO 世界冠军　首位亚太区选手夺冠</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/2024-pokemon-world-championships/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=2024-pokemon-world-championships</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/2024-pokemon-world-championships/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 05:14:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokemon GO]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257031</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港 16 岁少年郑业楷（绰号：虾皮）在 2024 年 Pokémon World Championships 的 Pokémon GO 赛事夺冠，成为首位赢得此项殊荣的香港选手，同时亦是亚太区首位世界冠军。虾皮在决赛中以 3 比 1 的成绩击败荷兰选手 Martijn Versteeg（Inadequance），赢得 20,000 美元（约港币 156,000 元）奖金。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">🎊 ATTENTION TRAINERS 🎊<br />
Yekai0904 is officially your <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/PokemonGO?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#PokemonGO</a> 2024 World Champion! 🏆 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/PokemonWorlds?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#PokemonWorlds</a><a href="https://t.co/j8hgapV6WM">pic.twitter.com/j8hgapV6WM</a></p><p>— Pokémon GO (@PokemonGoApp) <a href="https://twitter.com/PokemonGoApp/status/1825261934448460151?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 18, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>今届 Pokémon World Championships 于美国夏威夷檀香山举行，来自世界各地的训练员聚首一堂参与是次盛事。虾皮在比赛中展现出色表现，由区内比赛中脱颖而出，并在世界赛事中保持全胜纪录。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">First ever APAC GO Champion!!!<br />
Let’s goooooooon🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥</p><p>— Pui Pui Yekai0904 (@PYekai0904) <a href="https://twitter.com/PYekai0904/status/1825266689497559312?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 18, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>去年虾皮与其他香港选手代表亚太区参赛，但由于缺乏资助，需自行筹集旅费。幸得名医黎青龙等热心人士支持，他们得以参加日本横滨举办的比赛。虽然去年未能取得理想成绩，今年卷土重来，终在比赛中拔得头筹，为香港及亚太区争光。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240819125705-694x378.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="378" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240819125705-694x378.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240819125705.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=525326130069434">GO Taiwan@Facebook</a></p><p>虾皮赛后感谢一直支持他的家人、朋友及教练团队，并希望借此机会让更多人了解 Pokémon GO 这款游戏。他特别感激在香港的队友及对手 Martijn Versteeg，并表示通过比赛结识了世界各地的朋友，获益良多。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/wolrdchampionship202-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/wolrdchampionship202-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/wolrdchampionship202.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v">JonkusPKMN@YouTube</a></p><p>前香港 Pokémon GO 队伍领队 Sam 亦发文感谢团队，并提到教练 Aaron 在建立队伍作出的贡献，以及队长 Ivan 如何在虾皮低潮时给予他鼓励，让他最终能够重返赛场，并取得今天的成绩。虾皮曾透露，因为经济压力，他一度担心无法参赛，幸而在黎青龙等人的赞助下，最终得以站上世界舞台。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.i-cable.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/261477/">i-Cable</a>、<a href="https://www.am730.com.hk/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0/-16%E6%AD%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E5%93%A1%E8%B4%8Fpok%C3%A9mon-go%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E8%AA%AA%E5%9B%A0-%E5%86%87%E9%8C%A2-%E9%98%BF%E5%AA%BD%E5%94%94%E5%87%86%E5%8E%BB-/480286">am730</a>、<a href="https://x.com/pokemongoapp/status/1825261934448460151">PokemonGoApp@X</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/renewshk/photos/%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84-pok%C3%A9mon-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%B3%BDpok%C3%A9mon-world-championships%E4%B8%80%E9%80%A3%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%8F%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%B7%E6%AA%80%E9%A6%99%E5%B1%B1%E8%88%89%E8%BE%A6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E5%93%A116-%E6%AD%B2%E7%9A%84%E9%84%AD%E6%A5%AD%E6%A5%B7%E7%B6%BD%E8%99%9F%E8%9D%A6%E7%9A%AE%E5%9C%A8-pok%C3%A9/497378559714106/?paipv=0&amp;eav=AfaVUxZkplA7ZjICN_Po4tzzh0zRv9BdqSxbs3ChFXvSmeLwpCqtU-4XZ0DsmFwedIc&amp;_rdr">ReNews</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/EnglishLessonForFreedom">English Lesson for Freedom@Facebook</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/2024-pokemon-world-championships/game-channel/">香港 16 岁少年夺 Pokémon GO 世界冠军　首位亚太区选手夺冠</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
